### Backend — LLM Proxy Route

#### [NEW] [chat_routes.py](file:///d:/Project/Final_Year_Project/Interview_with_AI/app/routes/chat_routes.py)

New FastAPI router with:
- `POST /api/chat` — accepts `{ session_id, prompt }`
- Forwards prompt to Google Gemini API
- Logs `{ timestamp, prompt, response, token_count }` to MongoDB
- Returns AI response text

#### [NEW] [chat_service.py](file:///d:/Project/Final_Year_Project/Interview_with_AI/app/services/chat_service.py)

Business logic:
- Calls Google Gemini API using the `google-generativeai` SDK
- Extracts text response and token count
- Saves interaction log to `sessions` collection in MongoDB

#### [NEW] [chat_schema.py](file:///d:/Project/Final_Year_Project/Interview_with_AI/app/schemas/chat_schema.py)

Pydantic models:
- `ChatRequest` — validates `{ session_id: str, prompt: str }`
- `ChatResponse` — response structure `{ response: str, session_id: str }`

